## Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- NumPy >= 1.20.0
- SciPy >= 1.7.0
- Pandas >= 1.3.0
- For QGIS plugin: QGIS 3.0+

## Development

### Setting up Development Environment

```bash
git clone https://github.com/SanjeevBashyal/pymhm.git
cd pymhm
pip install -e .[dev]
```

### Running Tests

```bash
pytest
```

### Building Documentation

```bash
pip install -e .[docs]
sphinx-build -b html docs/ docs/_build/
```

